suite.doc:
TC002 — Login All Users, Add Product to Cart Twice, Remove All, Logout
Run AFTER TC001_Register.robot has completed.
Flow per user: 1. Open browser 2. Login 3. Search product → open detail → Add to cart (1st time) 4. Continue shopping → Search same product again → Add to cart (2nd time) (cart quantity update is disabled on this site so we add via search again) 5. Go to Cart → Verify product is present 6. Remove ALL items from cart 7. Verify cart is empty 8. Logout 9. Close browser
Run: robot --outputdir results testsTC002_Login.robot
